                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-806" type="surname" value="WELLS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-806" type="given" value="HANNAH"></interp>HANNAH WELLS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Edward Wells, office-keeper at the Metropolitan Stage-carriage Office. I went on board the Mercury steam. boat—I had a reticule with a bottle and knife-casein it—when we got to Woolwich I got up from my seat, and missed my bag—I looked round the vessel, and found the prisoner offering this spirit-bottle for sale—it is mine—I had drank about half of the spirits—he had been sitting close to me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
